class DefaultHome
extends com.vaadin.ui.CustomLayout

Mimics the Grails root index.gsp (i.e. showing Grails installation details, controllers etc.).

Uses the layout page 'home.html' in web-app/VAADIN/themes/{theme}/layouts.

Authors:
Francis
